                    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">10 Tips to Improve Your Coding Skills</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">Best Practices in Project Management</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://builtin.com/artificial-intelligence/artificial-intelligence-future" target="_blank">The Future of Artificial Intelligence</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- PDFs -->
            <div class="resource-item">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> PDFs</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/AmandaZou/Data-Science-books-/blob/master/Mastering%20Python%20for%20Data%20Science.pdf" target="_blank">Python for Data Science - Complete Guide</a></li>
